• Customize your background with cool filters and stickers.

• Large video wallpaper selection for all tastes and great quality.

Share & Set As:

3D Live Wallpapers in Ultra HD 4K - Transform Your Screen!

The 3D Live Wallpapers Ultra HD 4K app is here to revolutionize your home and lock screens. Explore a mesmerizing collection of 3D wallpapers, breathtaking 4K wallpapers, and dynamic live wallpapers that bring your device to life.

Live Wallpapers Ultra HD 4K Unleash the Power of Personalization
Dive into a world of cool wallpapers where every background is more than just an image. Our app offers a wide selection of live wallpapers that react to your touch and movements, providing an engaging and immersive experience every time you glance at your phone.

From sleek 4K wallpapers for a clean, high-resolution look to interactive 3D wallpapers that create depth and motion, there’s a wallpaper to match every mood and occasion.

3D Live Wallpapers Ultra HD 4K features:
🎨 Endless Customization:
Explore 18+ categories filled with over 1000 animated backgrounds, including themes like nature, space, AMOLED, gaming, anime, and more. These 4K wallpapers and live wallpapers are tailored to suit every taste.

✨ Advanced AI Integration:
Bring your imagination to life! Use our AI-powered tool to create unique, personalized wallpapers. Describe your idea, choose a style, and let the app transform it into an extraordinary 4K wallpaper.

🔥 Realistic Effects:
Enjoy video wallpapers with layered effects like rain, snow, fire, or smoke for an extra dimension of realism. The stunning 3D wallpapers feature actual depth, making characters and landscapes almost lifelike.

🔄 Auto-Changer Functionality:
Tired of the same look? Enable the auto-changer to rotate between your favorite live wallpapers every few hours, daily, or whenever you unlock your phone.

Standout Features
Dynamic 3D and 4K Wallpapers:
Make your screen pop with eye-catching visuals and smooth animations.

Battery Friendly Design:
Optimized to consume minimal power (0.5%–2%), our app ensures your device stays efficient while running beautiful live wallpapers.

Exclusive AMOLED Themes:
Take full advantage of your AMOLED screen with vibrant, deep black backgrounds that look stunning while conserving battery life.

Video as Wallpaper:
Turn your cherished videos into moving backgrounds and make every moment special.

Perfect Fit for Any Device:
From ultra-wide screens to compact displays, our wallpapers are designed to adjust automatically, offering a flawless fit for devices like Samsung Galaxy, Xiaomi, and OnePlus.

Create a Unique Experience with Live Wallpapers
Imagine unlocking your phone to find vivid, interactive animations of galaxies, epic superhero scenes, or serene natural landscapes. Our live wallpapers ensure every glance at your phone is a moment of joy.
Add depth to your screen with our 3D wallpapers, which create an incredible parallax effect. Or enjoy crisp, ultra-high-definition 4K wallpapers that bring unparalleled clarity and detail.

Stay Updated with Fresh Content
We regularly update the app with new cool wallpapers and themes. Discover trending designs, seasonal updates, and user-generated content to keep your screen fresh and unique.
Check out the public AI Gallery to see stunning wallpaper creations by other users and get inspired.

How to Use the 3D Live Wallpapers Ultra HD 4K App
Browse and Discover: Explore a variety of categories and pick your favorite 4K wallpaper, 3D wallpaper, or live wallpaper.
Preview and Set: Preview how the wallpaper will look on your home or lock screen.
Customize: Adjust effects and colors or create your wallpaper with our AI-powered tools.
Enjoy the Transformation: Set your chosen wallpaper and enjoy the stunning new look.

📥 Download Now and start exploring the world of cool wallpapers, live wallpapers, and vibrant 4K wallpapers that redefine what your phone can be.
